## 2. Сборка пакета

### `pyproject.toml`

```toml
[build-system]
requires = ["setuptools>=68", "wheel"]
build-backend = "setuptools.backends.legacy:build"

[project]
name = "minio-client"
version = "0.1.0"
description = "MinIO S3 client с поддержкой nginx subpath rewrite"
requires-python = ">=3.10"
dependencies = [
    "boto3>=1.28",
]

[project.optional-dependencies]
dev = ["pytest", "pytest-mock"]

[tool.setuptools.packages.find]
where = ["."]
include = ["minio_client*"]
```

